{"tid":118994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東區醫院17歲青年遭69歲男院友摸下體","createTime":"2017-02-13T12:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T00:35:02.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3034a9d076b1c9e6124501ecd2a0f2a229e9191a","tid":118994,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:02:52.000Z","msg":"受害人及男疑犯均為東院精神科男病人，男事主會見醫生投訴上周遭一名69歲男院友摸手腳及下體，因而揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n東區醫院發生懷疑風化案。下午3時許，柴灣樂民道東區醫院職員報案，稱一名69歲男子涉嫌非禮一名17歲青年，警方原列作求警協助，經調查後改列非禮，拘捕涉案69歲男子，帶返警署調查，交由東區刑事調查第一隊跟進。"},{"pid":"581f668af8b89358e89a88d6489dcaca49e64978","tid":118994,"uid":54778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308eab5e06b8fb263fba19a0dbe83ff340c21d94","tid":118994,"uid":38462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:04:57.000Z","msg":"青年？"},{"pid":"d8a696ce4b2b20cd993fa073cc8487f196ce59f8","tid":118994,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b00981e38a539b72d25202944f5cee59f2438c","tid":118994,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f2f513a626a71146889a523a2f14f31a1b102e","tid":118994,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:08:01.000Z","msg":"衣家啲幾十後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d223ed13ed076f051d1a3f741924d98da254961","tid":118994,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:08:24.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p